name: PR#2: Display start date, end date, and number of sections (weeks) on "Course Info" tab of instructor dashboard. (antoviaque) - antoviaque/edx-platform/OC-791-course-timeline (4095206)
vars_str:
# System
COMMON_HOSTNAME: 'pr2.sandbox.opencraft.com'

# edxapp
EDXAPP_PLATFORM_NAME: "PR#2: Display start date, end date, and number of sections (weeks) on "Course Info" tab of instructor dashboard. (antoviaque) - antoviaque/edx-platform/OC-791-course-timeline (4095206)"
EDXAPP_LMS_NGINX_PORT: 80
EDXAPP_LMS_PREVIEW_NGINX_PORT: 80
EDXAPP_CMS_NGINX_PORT: 80
EDXAPP_SITE_NAME: 'pr2.sandbox.opencraft.com'
EDXAPP_LMS_SITE_NAME: 'pr2.sandbox.opencraft.com'
EDXAPP_LMS_BASE: 'pr2.sandbox.opencraft.com'
EDXAPP_PREVIEW_LMS_BASE: 'pr2.sandbox.opencraft.com'

EDXAPP_CMS_SITE_NAME: 'studio.pr2.sandbox.opencraft.com'
EDXAPP_CMS_BASE: 'studio.pr2.sandbox.opencraft.com'

# Forum environment settings
FORUM_RACK_ENV: 'production'
FORUM_SINATRA_ENV: 'production'

# Emails
EDXAPP_CONTACT_EMAIL: 'contact@example.com'
EDXAPP_TECH_SUPPORT_EMAIL: 'contact@example.com'
EDXAPP_BUGS_EMAIL: 'contact@example.com'
EDXAPP_FEEDBACK_SUBMISSION_EMAIL: 'contact@example.com'
EDXAPP_DEFAULT_FROM_EMAIL: 'contact@example.com'
EDXAPP_DEFAULT_FEEDBACK_EMAIL: 'contact@example.com'
EDXAPP_SERVER_EMAIL: 'contact@example.com'
EDXAPP_BULK_EMAIL_DEFAULT_FROM_EMAIL: 'contact@example.com'

# Misc
EDXAPP_TIME_ZONE: 'UTC'

# Security updates
COMMON_SECURITY_UPDATES: true
SECURITY_UNATTENDED_UPGRADES: true
SECURITY_UPDATE_ALL_PACKAGES: false
SECURITY_UPGRADE_ON_ANSIBLE: true

# Repositories URLs
edx_ansible_source_repo: 'https://github.com/edx/configuration.git'
edx_platform_repo: 'https://github.com/antoviaque/edx-platform.git'

# Pin down dependencies to specific (known to be compatible) commits.
edx_platform_version: '40952060bc7573c5035620b985b211a24360f311'
configuration_version: 'master'
forum_version: 'master'
notifier_version: 'master'
xqueue_version: 'master'
certs_version: 'master'

# Features
EDXAPP_FEATURES:
 USE_MICROSITES: false
 AUTH_USE_OPENID: false
 ENABLE_DISCUSSION_SERVICE: true
 ENABLE_INSTRUCTOR_ANALYTICS: true
 ENABLE_INSTRUCTOR_EMAIL: true
 REQUIRE_COURSE_EMAIL_AUTH: false
 ENABLE_PEARSON_HACK_TEST: false
 SUBDOMAIN_BRANDING: false
 SUBDOMAIN_COURSE_LISTINGS: false
 PREVIEW_LMS_BASE: 'pr2.sandbox.opencraft.com'
 ENABLE_DJANGO_ADMIN_SITE: true
 ALLOW_ALL_ADVANCED_COMPONENTS: true
